From fbb6efb461de3ab08b2759074f29c8b36b228df4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dhanavandhana Kannan <dhanavan@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 2 Jun 2025 09:50:47 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL: hostapd: Add support to send
TTLM request action  frame

Add support to prepare TTLM element and send TTLM request action
frame from AP MLD as defined in IEEE P802.11be/D3.0 section 9.6.35.2
TID-To-Link Mapping Request frame format for negotiation of TTLM.

As negotiated TTLM is peer specific, tid to link mapping specific
structure is stored inside sta_info's mld_info structure as it holds
peer specific info.

Implemented TTLM specific handling and introduced TTLM specific
structures in ttlm.c and ttlm.h files.

Signed-off-by: Dhanavandhana Kannan <dhanavan@qti.qualcomm.com>
